### [Alpha] Updates project's network restrictions by adding or removing CIDRs
# @name v1-patch-network-restrictions
PATCH {{host}}/v1/projects/{{ref}}/network-restrictions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "add": {
    "dbAllowedCidrs": [
      "203.0.113.0/24"
    ]
  },
  "remove": {
    "dbAllowedCidrs": [
      "198.51.100.0/24"
    ]
  }
}

## Responses
# 200
# Content-Type: application/json
# 401
# Description: Unauthorized
# 403
# Description: Forbidden action
# 429
# Description: Rate limit exceeded
# 500
# Description: Failed to update project network restrictions

### Updates project's storage config
# @name v1-update-storage-config
PATCH {{host}}/v1/projects/{{ref}}/config/storage
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fileSizeLimit": 10485760,
  "features": {
    "imageTransformation": {
      "enabled": true
    }
  }
}

## Responses
# 401
# Description: Unauthorized
# 403
# Description: Forbidden action
# 429
